      <title>巴拿马矿山风险和供应短缺导致铜价升至 11 周高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/copper-climbs-to-11-week-high-on-panama-mine-risk-shortfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对巴拿马一座大型矿山即将关闭的担忧以及对 2024 年矿石供应缺口扩大的预期，铜价上涨至 11 周以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/copper-climbs-to-11-week-high-on-panama-mine-risk-shortfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 03:11:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈恩与消息人士称，公司正在考虑出售韩国 SK Shipping</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/hahn-co-weighs-sale-of-south-korea-s-sk-shipping-sources-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国收购公司 Hahn &amp;据知情人士透露，该公司正在审查其所持 SK Shipping Co. 多数股权的战略选择，包括出售该公司的债务，该公司的估值可能达到约 100 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/hahn-co-weighs-sale-of-south-korea-s-sk-shipping-sources-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 03:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港将于七月起结束台风期间股市休市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/hong-kong-to-end-stock-market-closures-during-typhoons-from-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于香港的股票交易员来说，台风的临近长期以来就意味着临时休息一天的预期。不再。该交易所运营商刚刚公布了一项在恶劣天气期间保持当地交易所开放的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/hong-kong-to-end-stock-market-closures-during-typhoons-from-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 03:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍克斯比表示，新西兰联储不能忽视移民激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/rbnz-can-t-afford-to-ignore-surging-immigration-hawkesby-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行副行长克里斯蒂安·霍克斯比表示，新西兰央行不能忽视移民激增，尽管移民潮预计明年将会消退，因为通胀长期以来一直高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/rbnz-can-t-afford-to-ignore-surging-immigration-hawkesby-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 00:18:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
